topics.body:
Pandora just started playing my misery song, "Ball and Chain by Social Distortion.":https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_NWjehpGSO0

What I mean by misery song is that this is the song I play when I'm feeling, depressed, run down, lonely, tired and I don't want anymore pain. Its this and Johnny Cash's cover of "Hurt":https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3aF9AJm0RFc because both accurately reflect how I feel when depressed, specifically just fucking tired and worn thin that I don't want to do anything.

For the record while I am indeed fucking tired and run down feeling today, that is entirely because I work in the hot sun all goddamn day and live in an area that is a fairly popular get away spot so everything was crowded as fuck with tourists.

This is not important though, what I'm asking is what is your misery song?
